Poznan - Birmingham Route from late December this year by WizzAir   
Sep 23, 2015 eTN   
WizzAir is about to expand its service operations at Birmingham by launching of 2nd Polish link form the 18th of December, 2015. The airline will be launching 2 weekly Poznan – Birmingham route, operating on Mondays and Fridays. 
Planned schedule: W61907 POZ0610 – 0730BHX 320 15 W61908 BHX0800 – 1110POZ 320 15
